                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Reid</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-11-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Reid reports that Lord Lansdowne has promised him that he will immediately
                    communicate with the colonial department and do everything possible.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
